---
// Componente About
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-secondary to-secondary/90"></div>
  
  <!-- Partículas decorativas -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-20 right-20 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-primary/30 opacity-20 animate-rotate-slow"></div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-40 left-20 w-32 h-32 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 opacity-30 animate-rotate-slow" style="animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 25s;"></div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/3 w-4 h-4 bg-primary/30 rounded-full opacity-70 animate-float"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Línea decorativa superior -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500/20 to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="text-white">Sobre</span>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-700"> Mí</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Desarrollador FullStack con pasión por la innovación tecnológica y el crecimiento profesional.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Marco decorativo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-blue-500/30 rounded-xl transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
          
          <!-- Card principal -->
          <div class="relative z-10 glass-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-blue-500/30">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg mr-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Perfil Profesional</h3>
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Soy un Desarrollador FullStack recién graduado de DAM (Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma) y técnico en SIR/SMX con 2.5 años de experiencia en Barcelona.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Actualmente trabajo como <span class="text-blue-400 font-medium">Desarrollador FullStack</span> en AgriNews, donde me estoy formando en <span class="text-blue-400 font-medium">.NET, IA y backend</span>. Mi objetivo es seguir creciendo profesionalmente y aportar soluciones innovadoras.
              </p>
              
              <div class="pt-6">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                  Habilidades personales
                </h4>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-colors flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Trabajo en equipo</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-colors flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Comunicación</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-colors flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Resolución de problemas</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-colors flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Adaptabilidad</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-blue-500/30 group">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-blue-900/30 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-blue-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Experiencia laboral</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              2.5 años de experiencia como desarrollador y administrador de sistemas, trabajando en diversas empresas y proyectos con tecnologías modernas.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-indigo-500/30 group">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-indigo-900/30 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-indigo-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z" />
                  <path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Formación académica</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Graduado en Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma (DAM) y técnico en Sistemas y Redes, con formación continua en tecnologías emergentes.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-purple-500/30 group">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-purple-900/30 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-purple-900/50 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Objetivos profesionales</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Especializarme en desarrollo full stack con tecnologías modernas, profundizando en la integración de IA en aplicaciones web y contribuir a proyectos innovadores.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 